title: BTS Reaction #1: Nudes (PJM Version)
body:
Disclaimer: this is a post of fiction, and so, is not real. I do not intend to cause any harm to the people who are involved.

Posted: 5th January 2019

MASTERLIST 

_____________________

The trembles running through your hands make it hard for you call your boyfriend. Your vision blurred from the tears flowing through them. Your chest hurts from crying and panicking. The phone placed to your ear and the ringing is barely heard through your erratic breathing and cries

“Hey (Y/N)! How are-“

“Jimin. Someone leaked my-my my nudes” you sob out 

“Your what?” He asks “but you’ve never sent me or shown me any” he retorts, you can hear the smirk in his voice. 

“No-o-othes-ss-e w-were from ss-school” 

“Wait what? What’s going on?” His voice is quiet 

“J-j-just look o-online” you whisper. The embarrassment takes the form of a flushed face: you were never known as ‘innocent’ but you were seen as not ‘innocent’ either.  Jimin saw you as a young, sweet girl, which you are but he did not once assume you would have sent those kinds of images before.  You can hear him rush to someone on the other side and he whines ‘Hyung please go online for a moment’ the two of the boys gasp at the same time ‘Is that (Y/N)?’ Yoongi, you assume, asks

“Oh my god, (Y/N), I’m so sorry, is there anything I can do?” The pained voice on the other end of the phone does little to comfort you

“Can you come here please?” For the first time, your voice didn’t fail you, a hum in acknowledgement and an ‘I’ll be back Hyung’ is heard before the line is dead. The black screen in your hand drops to the floor with a thump. Fresh tears flow down your cheeks as you collapse onto your knees; thankful you kicked all of your bedding onto the floor in frustration. The sobs leave your chest with an animalistic howl. Your fists ache as they continuously pound against the duvet. The situation sinking in for real now.

You woke up 15 minutes ago, and typically the first thing you do is check Twitter. As it turns out, an old friend of yours (who didn’t even have access to your old nudes anyway, so the confusion of this adds to your stress) decided to post your nudes from high school- which is technically illegal because you were underage in the picture- as a response to you apparently ‘taking everything she’s ever loved away’. You have not seen her or spoken to her in roughly, 7 years. 7 years. It is kind of bad that you forgot her name but now you could care less about her.

The front door opens and lets cold air flow into your living room. Jimin always teased you about how small your place was, but you were proud that was yours. His hair is slightly brittle against his hand: due to the rigorous amount of dye and bleach. His scarf falls to the floor next to his feet as he slips his boots off. Lastly, he places his coat on the back of your sofa as he glides by. The muffled sounds of your cries pain him: he hates seeing you upset. The situation you’re in is something neither of you two would have expected, so he knows not to pester you with a million and one questions. He stops outside your bedroom door and takes a deep breath

“(Y/N), baby are you in here?” His voice is soft yet slices through your sobs. Your eyes meet his form in the doorway, you leap up onto your feet and fling yourself into his form. His hands wrap around your back as he lets you cry into him. While Jimin himself is slightly shorter, you only come up to his shoulder: allowing him to feel as if he can protect you in his embrace. His body shakes with his own cries. 

“We can work through this okay my love? It may not seem like it right now, but I promise that things will work out eventually” his voice always manages to soothe you, right now not so much but you understand he’s trying his best. You mindlessly nod into him

“Do you want legal help? Do you want to prosecute anybody?” He inquires, his palms encase your face allowing you to look at him. Tears stain your face and your nose is running, you hiccup before responding

“I know exactly who did it, but I want time to think about it” you whimper out, he nods in acknowledgement.  

“I’m sorry. I didn’t mean for this to happen” you say and unintentionally spit at him “I’m sorry for that too”. Jimin faces crumple into a pathetic frown 

“You don’t have anything to apologise for, you didn’t do anything okay?” He responds placing a kiss to your forehead

summary: Storms are prettier in your eyes.
body:
Storms are prettier in your eyes.

[Short monologue]

Word count: 335

Uploaded on AO3

Summary:

jungkook has thought of quitting.

of course he has thought of leaving everything behind, let the constant ache in his bones win once and for all; remember how it is to have a nice and long night of sleep, without the suffocating voice inside his head telling him he was already late or having to do this or go there or-

yeah, he has thought of quitting.

but not after meeting yoongi.

Read complete at: https://archiveofourown.org/works/17308145
